dcterms:description: The UCF11 Dataset contains 1,600 video clips of a resolution 320 × 240 and is divided into 11 action categories. Each category consists of 25 groups of videos, within more than 4 clips in one group.

dcterms:description: Cifar10/100 consists of 50,000 train images and 10,000 test images with size as 32 × 32 × 3. CIFAR10 has 10 object classes and CIFAR100 has 100 categories.
